Simple Linear Regression

library(tidyverse)

Loading the dataset

data <- read_csv('data.csv')

 Column specification 
cols(
  TEMP = col_double(),
  ORDERS = col_double()
)

EDA

data %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=TEMP, y=ORDERS)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method='lm')

cor(data$TEMP, data$ORDERS)
[1] 0.906923

Modeling

mod <- lm(ORDERS ~ TEMP, data=data)
summary(mod)
